Azure ML Designer is a no-code/low-code, drag-and-drop tool within Azure Machine Learning that lets you build, train, 
and deploy machine learning models visually — without writing code. It’s especially useful for beginners, data analysts, or fast prototyping.

What You Can Do with Azure ML Designer:
Import and preprocess data

Drag and drop ML algorithms and modules

Train and validate models

Evaluate model performance

Deploy trained models as web services

Build ML pipelines visually
